      <title>英国的增长激增，工厂提高了美国关税的产出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/uk-growth-in-surprising-surge-ahead-of-trump-s-tariff-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国的经济在2月份的近一年中的增长最为强劲，因为工厂在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税浪潮中提高了生产，这些关税已将动荡带入了全球市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/uk-growth-in-surprising-surge-ahead-of-trump-s-tariff-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 06:05:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
