      <title>随着刺激，中国股票扩大了收益，Deal希望变得巨大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/chinese-stocks-end-three-day-winning-run-as-us-tariffs-hit-145</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股票正朝着为期四天的集会上，因为人们对更强大的刺激的期望，并希望与美国达成的贸易协定超过唐纳德·特朗普的145％关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/chinese-stocks-end-three-day-winning-run-as-us-tariffs-hit-145</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 01:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
